FBIS3-48093 "dreas015_c_94023" FBIS-EAS-94-015 Document Type:Daily Report 25 Jan 1994 North Korea WPK Greets British Communist Party Leader SK1601090194 Pyongyang KCNA in English 0807 GMT 16 Jan 94 SK1601090194 Pyongyang KCNA Language: English Article Type:BFN [Text] Pyongyang, January 16 (KCNA) -- The Central Committee of the Workers' Party of Korea [WPK] sent a message of greetings to Eric Trevett upon his reelection as general secretary of the Central Committee of the New Communist Party of Great Britain. Expressing the belief that the relations of friendship and cooperation between the two parties would continue to develop on good terms, the message wished the general secretary greater success in his responsible work for defending socialism and strengthening the party.
